{"ja524:0.1":"Jataka ","ja524:0.2":"Cattalisanipata ","ja524:0.3":"Tesakunavagga ","ja524:0.4":"4. Sankhapalajataka ","ja524:1.1":"“Ariyavakasosi pasannanetto, ","ja524:1.2":"Manne bhavam pabbajito kulamha; ","ja524:1.3":"Katham nu vittani pahaya bhoge, ","ja524:1.4":"Pabbaji nikkhamma ghara sapanna”. ","ja524:2.1":"“Sayam vimanam naradeva disva, ","ja524:2.2":"Mahanubhavassa mahoragassa; ","ja524:2.3":"Disvana punnana mahavipakam, ","ja524:2.4":"Saddhayaham pabbajitomhi raja”. ","ja524:3.1":"“Na kamakama na bhaya na dosa, ","ja524:3.2":"Vacam musa pabbajita bhananti; ","ja524:3.3":"Akkhahi me pucchito etamattham, ","ja524:3.4":"Sutvana me jayihitippasado”. ","ja524:4.1":"“Vanijja ratthadhipa gacchamano, ","ja524:4.2":"Pathe addasasimhi bhojaputte; ","ja524:4.3":"Pavaddhakayam uragam mahantam, ","ja524:4.4":"Adaya gacchante pamodamane. ","ja524:5.1":"Soham samagamma janinda tehi, ","ja524:5.2":"Pahatthalomo avacamhi bhito; ","ja524:5.3":"‘Kuhim ayam niyati bhimakayo, ","ja524:5.4":"Nagena kim kahatha bhojaputta’. ","ja524:6.1":"‘Nago ayam niyati bhojanattha, ","ja524:6.2":"Pavaddhakayo urago mahanto; ","ja524:6.3":"Sadunca thulanca mudunca mamsam, ","ja524:6.4":"Na tvam rasannasi videhaputta. ","ja524:7.1":"Ito mayam gantva sakam niketam, ","ja524:7.2":"Adaya satthani vikopayitva; ","ja524:7.3":"Mamsani bhokkhama pamodamana, ","ja524:7.4":"Mayanhi ve sattavo pannaganam’. ","ja524:8.1":"‘Sace ayam niyati bhojanattha, ","ja524:8.2":"Pavaddhakayo urago mahanto; ","ja524:8.3":"Dadami vo balibaddani solasa, ","ja524:8.4":"Nagam imam muncatha bandhanasma’. ","ja524:9.1":"‘Addha hi no bhakkho ayam manapo, ","ja524:9.2":"Bahu ca no uraga bhuttapubba; ","ja524:9.3":"Karoma te tam vacanam alara, ","ja524:9.4":"Mittanca no hohi videhaputta’. ","ja524:10.1":"Tadassu te bandhana mocayimsu, ","ja524:10.2":"Yam natthuto patimokkassa pase; ","ja524:10.3":"Mutto ca so bandhana nagaraja, ","ja524:10.4":"Pakkami pacinamukho muhuttam. ","ja524:11.1":"Gantvana pacinamukho muhuttam, ","ja524:11.2":"Punnehi nettehi palokayi mam; ","ja524:11.3":"Tadassaham pitthito anvagacchim, ","ja524:11.4":"Dasangulim anjalim paggahetva. ","ja524:12.1":"‘Gaccheva kho tvam taramanarupo, ","ja524:12.2":"Ma tam amitta punaraggahesum; ","ja524:12.3":"Dukkho hi luddehi puna samagamo, ","ja524:12.4":"Adassanam bhojaputtana gaccha’. ","ja524:13.1":"Agamasi so rahadam vippasannam, ","ja524:13.2":"Nilobhasam ramaniyam sutittham; ","ja524:13.3":"Samotatam jambuhi vetasahi, ","ja524:13.4":"Pavekkhi nittinnabhayo patito. ","ja524:14.1":"So tam pavissa na cirassa nago, ","ja524:14.2":"Dibbena me paturahum janinda; ","ja524:14.3":"Upatthahi mam pitaramva putto, ","ja524:14.4":"Hadayangamam kannasukham bhananto. ","ja524:15.1":"‘Tvam mesi mata ca pita alara, ","ja524:15.2":"Abbhantaro panadado sahayo; ","ja524:15.3":"Sakanca iddhim patilabhakosmi, ","ja524:15.4":"Alara passa me nivesanani; ","ja524:15.5":"Pahutabhakkham bahuannapanam, ","ja524:15.6":"Masakkasaram viya vasavassa. ","ja524:16.1":"Tam bhumibhagehi upetarupam, ","ja524:16.2":"Asakkhara ceva mudu subha ca; ","ja524:16.3":"Nicattina apparaja ca bhumi, ","ja524:16.4":"Pasadika yattha jahanti sokam. ","ja524:17.1":"Anavakula veluriyupanila, ","ja524:17.2":"Catuddisam ambavanam surammam; ","ja524:17.3":"Pakka ca pesi ca phala suphulla, ","ja524:17.4":"Niccotuka dharayanti phalani’. ","ja524:18.1":"Tesam vananam naradeva majjhe, ","ja524:18.2":"Nivesanam bhassarasannikasam; ","ja524:18.3":"Rajataggalam sovannamayam ularam, ","ja524:18.4":"Obhasati vijjurivantalikkhe. ","ja524:19.1":"Manimaya sonnamaya ulara, ","ja524:19.2":"Anekacitta satatam sunimmita; ","ja524:19.3":"Paripura kannahi alankatabhi, ","ja524:19.4":"Suvannakayuradharahi raja. ","ja524:20.1":"So sankhapalo taramanarupo, ","ja524:20.2":"Pasadamaruyha anomavanno; ","ja524:20.3":"Sahassathambham atulanubhavam, ","ja524:20.4":"Yatthassa bhariya mahesi ahosi. ","ja524:21.1":"Eka ca nari taramanarupa, ","ja524:21.2":"Adaya veluriyamayam mahaggham; ","ja524:21.3":"Subham manim jatimantupapannam, ","ja524:21.4":"Acodita asanamabbhihasi. ","ja524:22.1":"Tato mam urago hatthe gahetva, ","ja524:22.2":"Nisidayi pamukhaasanasmim; ","ja524:22.3":"‘Idamasanam atra bhavam nisidatu, ","ja524:22.4":"Bhavanhi me annataro garunam’. ","ja524:23.1":"Anna ca nari taramanarupa, ","ja524:23.2":"Adaya varim upasankamitva; ","ja524:23.3":"Padani pakkhalayi me janinda, ","ja524:23.4":"Bhariyava bhattu patino piyassa. ","ja524:24.1":"Apara ca nari taramanarupa, ","ja524:24.2":"Paggayha sovannamayaya patiya; ","ja524:24.3":"Anekasupam vividham viyanjanam, ","ja524:24.4":"Upanamayi bhatta manunnarupam. ","ja524:25.1":"Turiyehi mam bharata bhuttavantam, ","ja524:25.2":"Upatthahum bhattu mano viditva; ","ja524:25.3":"Tatuttarim mam nipati mahantam, ","ja524:25.4":"Dibbehi kamehi anappakehi. ","ja524:26.1":"‘Bhariya mameta tisata alara, ","ja524:26.2":"Sabbattamajjha padumuttarabha; ","ja524:26.3":"Alara etassu te kamakara, ","ja524:26.4":"Dadami te ta paricarayassu’. ","ja524:27.1":"Samvaccharam dibbarasanubhutva, ","ja524:27.2":"Tadassuham uttarimajjhabhasim; ","ja524:27.3":"‘Nagassidam kinti kathanca laddham, ","ja524:27.4":"Kathajjhagamasi vimanasettham. ","ja524:28.1":"Adhiccaladdham parinamajam te, ","ja524:28.2":"Sayankatam udahu devehi dinnam; ","ja524:28.3":"Pucchami tam nagarajetamattham, ","ja524:28.4":"Kathajjhagamasi vimanasettham’. ","ja524:29.1":"‘Nadhiccaladdham na parinamajam me, ","ja524:29.2":"Na sayankatam napi devehi dinnam; ","ja524:29.3":"Sakehi kammehi apapakehi, ","ja524:29.4":"Punnehi me laddhamidam vimanam’. ","ja524:30.1":"‘Kim te vatam kim pana brahmacariyam, ","ja524:30.2":"Kissa sucinnassa ayam vipako; ","ja524:30.3":"Akkhahi me nagarajetamattham, ","ja524:30.4":"Katham nu te laddhamidam vimanam’. ","ja524:31.1":"‘Raja ahosim magadhanamissaro, ","ja524:31.2":"Duyyodhano nama mahanubhavo; ","ja524:31.3":"So ittaram jivitam samviditva, ","ja524:31.4":"Asassatam viparinamadhammam. ","ja524:32.1":"Annanca pananca pasannacitto, ","ja524:32.2":"Sakkacca danam vipulam adasim; ","ja524:32.3":"Opanabhutam me gharam tadasi, ","ja524:32.4":"Santappita samanabrahmana ca. ","ja524:33.1":"Malanca gandhanca vilepananca, ","ja524:33.2":"Padipiyam yanamupassayanca; ","ja524:33.3":"Acchadanam seyyamathannapanam, ","ja524:33.4":"Sakkacca danani adamha tattha. ","ja524:34.1":"Tam me vatam tam pana brahmacariyam, ","ja524:34.2":"Tassa sucinnassa ayam vipako; ","ja524:34.3":"Teneva me laddhamidam vimanam, ","ja524:34.4":"Pahutabhakkham bahuannapanam; ","ja524:34.5":"Naccehi gitehi cupetarupam, ","ja524:34.6":"Ciratthitikam na ca sassatayam’. ","ja524:35.1":"‘Appanubhava tam mahanubhavam, ","ja524:35.2":"Tejassinam hanti atejavanto; ","ja524:35.3":"Kimeva dathavudha kim paticca, ","ja524:35.4":"Hatthattamagacchi vanibbakanam. ","ja524:36.1":"Bhayam nu te anvagatam mahantam, ","ja524:36.2":"Tejo nu te nanvagam dantamulam; ","ja524:36.3":"Kimeva dathavudha kim paticca, ","ja524:36.4":"Kilesamapajji vanibbakanam’. ","ja524:37.1":"‘Na me bhayam anvagatam mahantam, ","ja524:37.2":"Tejo na sakka mama tehi hantum; ","ja524:37.3":"Satanca dhammani sukittitani, ","ja524:37.4":"Samuddavelava duraccayani. ","ja524:38.1":"Catuddasim pancadasim alara, ","ja524:38.2":"Uposatham niccamupavasami; ","ja524:38.3":"Athagamum solasa bhojaputta, ","ja524:38.4":"Rajjum gahetvana dalhanca pasam. ","ja524:39.1":"Bhetvana nasam atikassa rajjum, ","ja524:39.2":"Nayimsu mam samparigayha ludda; ","ja524:39.3":"Etadisam dukkhamaham titikkham, ","ja524:39.4":"Uposatham appatikopayanto’. ","ja524:40.1":"‘Ekayane tam pathe addasamsu, ","ja524:40.2":"Balena vannena cupetarupam; ","ja524:40.3":"Siriya pannaya ca bhavitosi, ","ja524:40.4":"Kim patthayam naga tapo karosi’. ","ja524:41.1":"‘Na puttahetu na dhanassa hetu, ","ja524:41.2":"Na ayuno capi alara hetu; ","ja524:41.3":"Manussayonim abhipatthayano, ","ja524:41.4":"Tasma parakkamma tapo karomi’. ","ja524:42.1":"‘Tvam lohitakkho vihatantaramso, ","ja524:42.2":"Alankato kappitakesamassu; ","ja524:42.3":"Surosito lohitacandanena, ","ja524:42.4":"Gandhabbarajava disa pabhasasi. ","ja524:43.1":"Deviddhipattosi mahanubhavo, ","ja524:43.2":"Sabbehi kamehi samangibhuto; ","ja524:43.3":"Pucchami tam nagarajetamattham, ","ja524:43.4":"Seyyo ito kena manussaloko’. ","ja524:44.1":"‘Alara nannatra manussaloka, ","ja524:44.2":"Suddhi va samvijjati samyamo va; ","ja524:44.3":"Ahanca laddhana manussayonim, ","ja524:44.4":"Kahami jatimaranassa antam’. ","ja524:45.1":"‘Samvaccharo me vasato tavantike, ","ja524:45.2":"Annena panena upatthitosmi; ","ja524:45.3":"Amantayitvana palemi naga, ","ja524:45.4":"Cirappavutthosmi aham janinda’. ","ja524:46.1":"‘Putta ca dara anujivino ca, ","ja524:46.2":"Niccanusittha upatitthathetam; ","ja524:46.3":"Kaccinnu tam nabhisapittha koci, ","ja524:46.4":"Piyanhi me dassanam tuyham alara’. ","ja524:47.1":"‘Yathapi matu ca pitu agare, ","ja524:47.2":"Putto piyo pativihito vaseyya; ","ja524:47.3":"Tatopi mayham idhameva seyyo, ","ja524:47.4":"Cittanhi te naga mayi pasannam’. ","ja524:48.1":"‘Mani mamam vijjati lohitanko, ","ja524:48.2":"Dhanaharo maniratanam ularam; ","ja524:48.3":"Adaya tvam gaccha sakam niketam, ","ja524:48.4":"Laddha dhanam tam manimossajassu’. ","ja524:49.1":"Dittha maya manusakapi kama, ","ja524:49.2":"Asassata viparinamadhamma; ","ja524:49.3":"Adinavam kamagunesu disva, ","ja524:49.4":"Saddhayaham pabbajitomhi raja. ","ja524:50.1":"Dumapphalaniva patanti manava, ","ja524:50.2":"Dahara ca vuddha ca sarirabheda; ","ja524:50.3":"Etampi disva pabbajitomhi raja, ","ja524:50.4":"Apannakam samannameva seyyo”. ","ja524:51.1":"“Addha have sevitabba sapanna, ","ja524:51.2":"Bahussuta ye bahuthanacintino; ","ja524:51.3":"Naganca sutvana tavancalara, ","ja524:51.4":"Kahami punnani anappakani”. ","ja524:52.1":"“Addha have sevitabba sapanna, ","ja524:52.2":"Bahussuta ye bahuthanacintino; ","ja524:52.3":"Naganca sutvana mamanca raja, ","ja524:52.4":"Karohi punnani anappakani”ti. ","ja524:53.1":"Sankhapalajatakam catuttham. "}